{"id":163318,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/06/global-voices-新加坡：因高龄病患受虐而怒/","date":"2011-06-23T16:30:32Z","modified":"2011-06-23T16:30:32Z","title":"Global Voices | 新加坡：因高龄病患受虐而怒","content":"<p><p>虽然安养院名为“南丁格尔”，但其中部分护士似乎没有如南丁格尔（Florence Nightingale）般的牺牲奉献精神。</p>\n<p>上星期有段偷拍画面曝光，记录安养院里一名75岁妇人遭虐待，让新加坡社会既震惊又愤怒，<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=c7kkJ2Glxko&#038;feature=related\" href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=c7kkJ2Glxko&#038;feature=related\">影片</a>拍下护士掌掴躺在床上的高龄病患：</p>\n</p>\n<p>许多新加坡民众要求惩处暴力护士，<em>Javert&#8217;s World</em><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://javertworld.blogspot.com/2011/06/hopeless-moh.html\" href=\"http://javertworld.blogspot.com/2011/06/hopeless-moh.html\">表示</a>：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>大众有权得知员工受到什么处罚，也许只是口头警告吗？安养院院长也不该幸免，受害人及其家属也应获得补偿。</p>\n<p>此事可能发生在任何人身上，却真的在新加坡出现，令我相当失望。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://whenthespinstops.blogspot.com/2011/06/nightingale-and-other-stories.html\" href=\"http://whenthespinstops.blogspot.com/2011/06/nightingale-and-other-stories.html\">Reuben Chan</a>指出，新加坡只有少数民众愿意照顾年迈亲人：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>若高龄者照顾工作全都委外，由临时工承接新加坡国民不愿费力的工作，各位还有何期待？看护工这项职业并不光鲜，国内民众也不想从 事，只想担任又体面又富有的医师，但不愿成为擦拭病患臀部的护士。看护必须面对许多子女排斥的脾气暴躁长者，若看护所见，子女都不愿尊重这些高龄者，他们 又何必毕恭毕敬？并非每个人都是南丁格尔或格蕾莎修女。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><em>Loh and behold</em>怀疑，其他安养院也有<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://lohandbehold.com/2011/06/12/nightingale-nursing-home-shut-it-down-prosecute-the-management-lock-them-up-throw-away-the-key/\" href=\"http://lohandbehold.com/2011/06/12/nightingale-nursing-home-shut-it-down-prosecute-the-management-lock-them-up-throw-away-the-key/\">虐待案例</a>：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>我们应该揪出南丁格尔安养院背后的蠢蛋，然后像他们对待那位可怜老妇人一样，把这些人扔入大牢，永远不准出狱。</p>\n<p>究竟得发生几件虐待案，政府才会有所作为？</p>\n<p>在这种安养院里，多是未受教育的痴呆患者，其中多么可怕实在难以想像。</p>\n<p>我确信还有其他大众不知道的虐待案例。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>后来发现，影片中受虐妇人的儿子早在<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://www.temasekreview.com/2011/06/11/moh-refuses-to-take-action-against-abusive-nursing-aides/\" href=\"http://www.temasekreview.com/2011/06/11/moh-refuses-to-take-action-against-abusive-nursing-aides/\">三个多月前</a>，便已向卫生单位通报，有些作家指称，政府在上个月大选之前<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://www.temasekreview.com/2011/06/11/health-minister-apologizes-but-son-now-defends-nursing-home/\" href=\"http://www.temasekreview.com/2011/06/11/health-minister-apologizes-but-son-now-defends-nursing-home/\">刻意掩盖此事</a>。</p>\n<p>之后政府暂时禁止该院接受新病患，<em>mrbrown.com</em>认为，安养院只受到这种惩罚<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://www.mrbrown.com/blog/2011/06/nightingale-nursing-home-mistreats-patient.html?utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+mrbrown+%28mrbrown%29\" href=\"http://www.mrbrown.com/blog/2011/06/nightingale-nursing-home-mistreats-patient.html?utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+mrbrown+%28mrbrown%29\">实在太奇怪</a>：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>没有人遭到起诉，没有人因此丢掉工作，安养院也只是暂时不得接受新病患。</p>\n<p>太可恶了。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Twitter和Facebook网站也有各种反应：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://www.twitter.com/Evan_Lby\" href=\"http://www.twitter.com/Evan_Lby\">@Evan_Lby</a>：南丁格尔安养院要培育新一代新加坡摔角手吗？不仅把老人家丢在床上，还甩耳光…</p>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=610574076\" href=\"http://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=610574076\">Chan CL</a>：卫生部应关闭这间安养院，安养院名称只是种反讽。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>此事也让众人开始讨论新加坡<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://www.yoursdp.org/index.php/perspective/special-feature/4859-rethinking-healthcare-financing-in-singapore-part-1\" href=\"http://www.yoursdp.org/index.php/perspective/special-feature/4859-rethinking-healthcare-financing-in-singapore-part-1\">医疗品质</a>，Therese Leung与Sumytra Menon分析该采取哪些措施，才能改善国内<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://www.todayonline.com/Singapore/EDC110613-0000011/Who-will-look-after-our-elderly\" href=\"http://www.todayonline.com/Singapore/EDC110613-0000011/Who-will-look-after-our-elderly\">高龄者</a>医疗服务：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>长期而言，新加坡必须重新规划制度，让本地劳工愿意从事长期照顾工作，才能降低依赖外藉劳工的程度，我们建议在薪资、职涯发展、监督方面都需要调整。</p>\n<p>研究显示，提高薪资能吸引与留住本地长期照顾产业劳工，所谓调涨薪水并非给予单次加给，而是依据年资与经验，提供不同等级的薪资。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>两人指称，目前新加坡65岁以上人口占全国的十二分之一，但到2030年，比例会增至五分之一。</p>\n<div>校对：<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"使用者:Soup\" href=\"http://proj.daodin.net/mediawiki/index.php/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E8%80%85:Soup\">Soup</a></div>\n<p><span>作者 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/author/mong/\" title=\"文章导读 Mong Palatino\">Mong Palatino</a> · 译者 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://zh.globalvoicesonline.org/hans/author/leonard/\" title=\"文章导读 Leonard\">Leonard</a> </span> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/2011/06/14/singapore-anger-over-mistreatment-of-elderly-patient/\" title=\"阅读原文 [en]\">阅读原文 [en]</a> · <span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://zh.globalvoicesonline.org/hans/2011/06/23/9401/#comments\" title=\"则留言\">则留言 (0) </a></span><br />分享: <span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.hemidemi.com/user_bookmark/new?title=%E6%96%B0%E5%8A%A0%E5%9D%A1%EF%BC%9A%E5%9B%A0%E9%AB%98%E9%BE%84%E7%97%85%E6%82%A3%E5%8F%97%E8%99%90%E8%80%8C%E6%80%92&#038;url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2011%2F06%2F23%2F9401%2F&#038;description=&#038;via=sticker\" title=\"HEMiDEMi\"><span>HEMiDEMi</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://myshare.url.com.tw/index.php?func=newurl&#038;url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2011%2F06%2F23%2F9401%2F&#038;desc=%E6%96%B0%E5%8A%A0%E5%9D%A1%EF%BC%9A%E5%9B%A0%E9%AB%98%E9%BE%84%E7%97%85%E6%82%A3%E5%8F%97%E8%99%90%E8%80%8C%E6%80%92\" title=\"MyShare\"><span>MyShare</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.shouker.com/%22%20onclick=%22javascript:var%20js=document.createElement%20(\" title=\"Shouker\"><span>Shouker</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.facebook.com/share.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2011%2F06%2F23%2F9401%2F\" title=\"facebook\"><span>facebook</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://twitter.com/share?